    "title": "TVTime - Shows Tracker",
    "description": "<p>A TV Shows organizer to track and find information about any TV Show.</p> <p>This project utilizes the Firebase Database for login/signup and storing user data. The app fetches all the necessary information from various APIs: <a className='api-links' target='_blank' href='https://developer.themoviedb.org/docs'>TheMovieDB API</a> for TV show details, the <a className='api-links' target='_blank' href='https://rapidapi.com/linaspurinis/api/mdblist/'>MDBList API</a> for TV show ratings, and the <a className='api-links' target='_blank' href='https://rapidapi.com/movie-of-the-night-movie-of-the-night-default/api/streaming-availability'>Streaming Availability API</a> for TV show streaming availability in the user's country.</p>",
